            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text presents different perspectives of human beings on people around the world. For better understanding, we recommend reviewing the sections *First Steps;*, *Understanding Texts* and *Atlas* (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
