            },
            {
               "text": "<p style=\"margin: auto; width: 100%;\"><iframe src=\"https://archive.org/details/in.gov.ignca.16173/page/n241/mode/2up\" width=\"100%\" height=\"560\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"true\" mozallowfullscreen=\"true\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Livro 1</b>: Ibn Khaldūn, Muqaddimah uma introdução a história, Volume 1</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p>Despite nearly a millennium separating the fall of the Roman Empire from Ibn Khaldūn’s writings, there is a striking resemblance between Rome’s attempt to distance itself from the “barbarians” (<htcite0>) and the Arab view of distinguishing sub-Saharan Africa from regions under Arab cultural influence (<htcite1>).</p><p>Thus, the idea of superiority was deeply rooted in Eurasia for centuries, especially among neighboring peoples. It is therefore unsurprising that this mindset persisted in encounters with the unknown.</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "7b9c164d-a727-49f1-8bad-53b0619812ff",
                     "text": "Devallet, Suzanne",
                     "page": "pp. 112",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2008",
                        "month": "10",
                        "day": "29"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a893dd90-f199-4a89-a82a-d0bcb25bf2a6",
                     "text": "Rosenthal, Franz",
                     "page": "pp. 119",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "1958",
                        "month": "06",
                        "day": "23"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2008",
