      {
         "id": "SECTION_meeting",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>The Encounter with the Unknown</h3>Although colonizers mistreated Indigenous peoples throughout the American continent (<i>Abya Yala</i>), this text focuses on two specific cases: Franciscans in Yucatán, Mexico, and Jesuits in the Captaincy of São Vicente, Brazil.</p><p>In Yucatán, Diego de Landa’s actions against the Maya have been widely recorded. Among the atrocities were:<ul><li>Use of torture (<htcite0>).</li><li>Burning of Maya codices (<htcite1>; <htcite2>).</li></ul></p><p>According to Timmer (<htcite3>) these actions were motivated by an apocalyptic worldview. Segrest (<htcite4>), meanwhile, argues that beyond “idolatry” as defined by Christian interpretation, there was also a belief in Indigenous inferiority—echoing perspectives similar to those of Ibn Khaldūn (<htcite5>).</div></div></p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b7fa522f-cdc0-47e1-b0a5-049a2bb463db",
                     "text": "Timmer, David E.",
                     "page": "pp. 477-478",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "1997",
                        "month": "04",
                        "day": "26"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b7fa522f-cdc0-47e1-b0a5-049a2bb463db",
                     "text": "Timmer, David E.",
                     "page": "pp. 479-480",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "1997",
                        "month": "04",
                        "day": "26"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "6b63a795-3240-40d3-9248-465d75cf469e",
                     "text": "Segrest, Colt",
                     "page": "pp. 32-36",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2018",
                        "month": "10",
                        "day": "29"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b7fa522f-cdc0-47e1-b0a5-049a2bb463db",
                     "text": "Timmer, David E.",
                     "page": "pp. 485-488",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "1997",
                        "month": "04",
